&lt;li>
&lt;p>windows11 官方&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/software-download/windows11" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>下载地址&lt;/a>, 选择对应iso以后按照提示选择即可下载&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://imhy.top/post/environment/images/download_w11.png"
loading="lazy"
alt="windows11 下载截图"
>&lt;/p>
